{
  "id": "impress_conference_talk_from_outline",
  "app": "libreoffice_impress",
  "task": "/home/user/Documents/talk_skeleton.odp is open in LibreOffice Impress — a 3-slide skeleton with titles 'Motivation', 'Approach', 'Evaluation' and empty bodies.\n\nFill in body content for the three existing slides and add three new slides so the final 6-slide deck is:\n\n1. 'Motivation' — body 'Current tools do not scale to petabyte datasets'\n2. 'Approach' — body 'Tiered storage with vector indexing'\n3. 'Evaluation' — body 'Benchmarked on TPC-H at 10TB'\n4. 'Related Work' (new) — body 'Comparison with Dremel and Presto'\n5. 'Limitations' (new) — body 'Cold start latency remains high'\n6. 'Future Work' (new) — body 'Adaptive query planning'\n\nSave the file, overwriting /home/user/Documents/talk_skeleton.odp and keeping the .odp format. The deck must have exactly 6 slides.",
  "env": {
    "files": [
      {
        "filename": "talk_skeleton.odp",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Documents/talk_skeleton.odp"
      }
    ]
  },
  "verification": [
    {
      "command": "check-slide-count 6",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Exactly 6 slides"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-title 0 \"Motivation\"",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 1 title preserved"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-contains 0 \"Current tools do not scale to petabyte datasets\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 1 body filled"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-title 1 \"Approach\"",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 2 title preserved"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-contains 1 \"Tiered storage with vector indexing\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 2 body filled"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-title 2 \"Evaluation\"",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 3 title preserved"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-contains 2 \"Benchmarked on TPC-H at 10TB\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 3 body filled"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-title 3 \"Related Work\"",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 4 new"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-contains 3 \"Comparison with Dremel and Presto\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 4 body"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-title 4 \"Limitations\"",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 5 new"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-contains 4 \"Cold start latency remains high\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 5 body"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-title 5 \"Future Work\"",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 6 new"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-slide-contains 5 \"Adaptive query planning\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Slide 6 body"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-exists /home/user/Documents/talk_skeleton.odp",
      "key": "exists",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "File saved"
    }
  ],
  "metadata": {
    "complexity": 5,
    "data_generatability": 5,
    "verification_determinism": 5,
    "estimated_difficulty": 5
  }
}
